{"tid":1393120,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚阻住我，8月5號我要返工！","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T05:37:45.000Z","uid":20948,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4719d8b5428819db5e079e0d6d0422f3b1cb3c7b","tid":1393120,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:45:11.000Z","msg":"作爲一個熱愛返工嘅打工仔，我無時無刻都想返工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日八號風球都照返工！戴住頭盔返工！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地班仆街唔好阻住我下星期繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以你地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好散播謠言，話有人會帶炸彈，大殺傷力武器，無差別攻擊！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因爲如果係咁，我當日就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一定唔會返工</span></span>！因爲我要留返我嘅有用之軀以後繼續返工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且我有機會出信俾HR，叫全公司唔好返工！因爲有同事受傷，會影響我日後工作進度！<br />\n<br />\n我再講多次，唔好搞到我冇得返工！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d983729f756da0031b9617336185207fe7cdb671","tid":1393120,"uid":20948,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:47:17.000Z","msg":"if you stop me from farn gong !<br />\nyour spring pocket will be barbecued !"},{"pid":"818c88a01c3ef0c22295cf3fd177c081de6d46d4","tid":1393120,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123040f0fb7feb71ee48b197c6b79c4414b96dbc","tid":1393120,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"